{"tha-ap300:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap300:0.2":"Citakapujakavagga ","tha-ap300:0.3":"Saranagamaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap300:1.1":"“Pabbate himavantamhi, ","tha-ap300:1.2":"ahosim luddako tada; ","tha-ap300:1.3":"Vipassim addasam buddham, ","tha-ap300:1.4":"lokajettham narasabham. ","tha-ap300:2.1":"Upasitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap300:2.2":"veyyavaccamakasaham; ","tha-ap300:2.3":"Sarananca upagacchim, ","tha-ap300:2.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap300:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap300:3.2":"saranam upagacchaham; ","tha-ap300:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap300:3.4":"saranagamanapphalam. ","tha-ap300:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap300:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap300:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap300:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saranagamaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap300:6.1":"Saranagamaniyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}